text: KJZT-LP (90.1 FM, "Jazz Tulsa") is an American low-power radio station in Tulsa, Oklahoma broadcasting a smooth jazz format. ==History== The station started as "Jazz Tulsa 107.9". ==References== ==External links== * JZT-LP JZT- LP Category:Jazz radio stations in the United States Category:Radio stations established in 2005
